Authorization.invalidLogin: Tvoje geslo in/ali e-poštni naslov nista veljavna. Poskusi znova.

ForgotPassword.instructions: Vnesi e-poštni naslov računa. Poslana bo povezava za ponastavitev gesla.
ForgotPassword.successInstructions2: klikni na povezavo. Preusmerili te bomo na stran, kjer lahko ponastaviš svoje geslo.
ForgotPassword.resendInstructions: Če nisi prejel e-pošte, pritisni gumb 'ponovno pošlji'

Admins.noListDataDescription: Lahko dodajš več Adminov. Admins bodo odgovorni za nadzor vsebine za Stranke in dodajanje Storitev.
Admins.addAdminDescription: Upoštevaj, da bo <important>Admin prejel e-poštno povabilo,</important> ki mu bo omogočilo dostop do nadzorne plošče.

Clients.noListDataDescription: Tukaj boš videl seznam vseh strank. Stranke imajo mandat za ogled podatkov, ki jih dodajajo Admins in Storitve, prav tako dodajajo povratne informacije za storitve in objavljajo nove naročila.
Clients.addClientDescription: Upoštevaj, da bo <important>uporabnik prejel e-poštno povabilo,</important> ki mu bo omogočilo dostop do nadzorne plošče.

Services.noListDataDescription: Tukaj lahko upravljaš vse storitve, ki so vključene v posel. Storitve lahko vključujejo vse storitve, ki jih ponuja posel ali so potrebne za posel.
Services.addServiceDescription: Dodaj novo storitev. Storitve pomagajo organizirati in kategorizirati različne vrste zagotovljene podpore in oskrbe.

Buy.deleteDescription: Press 'Delete' if you want to remove the Buy entry.
Buy.noListDataDescription: Here you can manage all the buy-related records that are included in the business.
Buy.addDescription: Add a new buy entry. Use this section to track buy-focused opportunities.

Rent.deleteDescription: Press 'Delete' if you want to remove the Rent entry.
Rent.noListDataDescription: Here you can manage all the rent-related records that are included in the business.
Rent.addDescription: Add a new rent entry. Use this section to track rent-focused opportunities.

Events.deleteDescription: Press 'Delete' if you want to remove the Event.
Events.noListDataDescription: Here you can manage all the events that are included in the business.
Events.addDescription: Add a new event. Use this section to organize and track events.

Orders.deleteDescription: Press 'Delete' if you want to remove the Order.
Orders.noListDataDescription: Here you can manage all the orders that are included in the business.
Orders.addDescription: Add a new order. Use this section to track incoming orders.

Settings.emailVerificationDialogDescription: Potrdi posodobljeno e-pošto. Po potrditvi tvoje e-pošte se prijavi, da jo posodobiš v svojih nastavitvah.
